io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.resourcepack

Class ResourcepackWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.resourcepack.ResourcepackWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PackHolder, PackWrapper, org.bukkit.configuration.serialization.ConfigurationSerializable

    public class ResourcepackWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements PackWrapper
    The resourcepack wrapper which can be used to wrap sound files and be hosted as a file. It has the ability to modify the base resourcepack file as well as the sounds.json file. You may also specify other attributes such as the icon, description, and format.
